{
  "stem": "25809.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we knew that there was no way to escape them, unless we got in time into the hiding place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we-- we watched them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And lit--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We watched the Germans setting up barricades and blocking the roads.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we watched them, and at first, they were on one side of the canal-- the right side of the canal from our position, away from us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we saw them hauling people out of homes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a terrible experience, just watching how they were dragging people out of the homes and putting them in trucks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the trucks would drive away with all the people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would be-- it was just-- the fear in the house was-- you could have cut it with a knife, because we we're afraid that they were going to continue.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Luckily, they stopped right at that bridge, and they didn't go into the west end and check the west end out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we cleared that hurdle, and we all sighed with relief, ay yi yi, thank God and whatever more.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we got-- we did not get caught in that crunch or raid-- as you-- they called it Razia-- in that raid, as you might say.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, yeah, a few months later-- I don't exactly remember when-- I think it was around about September of '42 or so, it must have been-- we were all, after-- after dinner we were just sitting around a table, talking in general, and, yeah, nothing much happening.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I didn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a very good question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but how is it to live like that?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a matter of no choice.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
